      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Media Processing & Publishing Phase\n**Nodes Involved**: Download Product Image → Facebook Publishing → Instagram Rate Limit Check → Instagram Media Container → Instagram Error Handling → Instagram Post Publication\n\n**What Happens**:\n- Downloads high-quality product image from your website\n- Publishes to Facebook page with longer-form content and image\n- Checks Instagram daily posting limits (max 20 posts/day via API)\n- Creates Instagram media container with optimized content and hashtags\n- Handles any Instagram API errors gracefully\n- Publishes final Instagram post if within rate limits",
